# Roundhouse Duo @ West Hills
Sat, Apr 26
| 
West Hills Vineyards
Come enjoy the smooth sounds of Roundhouse Duo live in our tasting room! Let their captivating acoustic melodies set the perfect backdrop as you sip on our finest selections. It’s an evening of great music, great drinks, and even better company—join us for a memorable experience! ## Time & Location
Apr 26, 2025, 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM
West Hills Vineyards, 4785 Salem Dallas Hwy NW, Salem, OR 97304, USA
